<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>로그인 페이지</title>
    <!-- 부트스트랩 CSS 링크 -->
    <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script
            src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: rgb(32, 36, 41);
        }
        .container {
            min-width: 640px;
            width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .login__container {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .text__title .social-icons img {
            width: 40px;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .back {
            width: 100%;
            height: 64px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 243, 245);
        }
        .back svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        .utility {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .utility a {
            display: block;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .social__icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0px 38px;
            margin: 22px 0px 59px;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .social__icons a {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login__btn {
            display: flex;

            align-items: center;

            vertical-align: middle;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
            border: none;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: rgb(32, 36, 41);
            color: white;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn__update {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            height: 52px;
        }
        .text__title .text__box {
            width: 40%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .text__title .text__box h3 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 34px;
        }
        .line__box {
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .line__box .line {
            width: 100%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 243, 245);

            border-collapse: collapse;
            position: relative;
        }
        .line__box .line p {
            background-color: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="back">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512">
            <!--!Font Awesome Free 6.6.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.-->
            <path
                    d="M9.4 233.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l192 192c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L77.3 256 246.6 86.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-192 192z"
            />
        </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="login__container">
        <div class="text__title">
            <div class="text__box">
                <h3>안녕하세요</h3>
                <h3>FilmTalk 입니다.</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
                하이브, 브랜덤, 셉피, 서울스토어의 통합회원으로<br />
                로그인이 가능합니다.
            </p>
        </div>

        <form
                action="/login"
                method="post"
                enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
        >
            <div class="form-group mb-3">
                <input
                        type="text"
                        class="form-control"
                        placeholder="Enter username"
                        name="username"
                        value="ssar"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group mb-3">
                <input
                        type="password"
                        class="form-control"
                        placeholder="Enter password"
                        name="password"
                        value="1234"
                />
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn__update form-control">
                로그인
            </button>
        </form>

        <div class="utility">
            <a class="text" href="#">아이디 찾기</a>
            <a class="text" href="#">비밀번호 찾기</a>
            <a class="text" href="#">회원가입</a>
        </div>

        <div class="line__box">
            <div class="line">
                <p>SNS 계정으로 로그인</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="social__icons">
            <a href="#"><img src="/img/ic_facebook.svg" alt="Facebook " /></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="/img/ic_kakao.svg" alt="Kakao" /></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="/img/ic_google.svg" alt="Google" /></a>
            <a href="#"><img src="/img/ic_naver.svg" alt="Naver" /></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 부트스트랩 JS 링크 -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
